text: Dancehall Queen is a 1997 Jamaican film. Dancehall Queen may also refer to: * "Dancehall Queen", a song by Beenie Man in the film * "Dancehall Queen" (Robyn song), a 2010 song by Robyn * Dancehall Queens, female celebrities in the dancehall music genre == See also == * Lady Saw (born 1968), Jamaican reggae singer known as the queen of dancehall
